CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1945, p. 28, reads: Charming Misses Honored - Graduates from Schenley High School were honored Monday evening at Loendi Club, at a party given by their parents.  Sharing honors were Misses Elaine Davis, Beverly Moss, W. Frances Kelly, Rosemarie Lawrence, Lois Weaver, Eugenia Scott, Charlotte Primas, Myrna Parks, Doris Clark and Juanita Taylor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Schenley High School graduates seated from left: Juanita Taylor, Doris Clark, Eugenia Scott, Beverly Moss; standing: Lois Weaver (Watson), Myrna Parks, Elaine Davis, Charlotte Primas, Rosemarie Lawrence, and W. Frances Kelly, posed in Loendi Club
